{"tid":1263983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未登記選民快d去登記 7月2日截止","createTime":"2019-06-28T12:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:40:47.000Z","uid":251082,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3cba96dc18c5d81ecf8e3a3521dcabe862aa3940","tid":1263983,"uid":251082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"已經登記咗都要去查下啲資料啱唔啱<br />\n好多人都話冇咗選民記錄 大家都要check下 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fcheckvrstatus.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=2d252d03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/checkvrstatus.htm</a><br />\n或者打電話28911001 &gt; 1 &gt; 2去查 扮工時間9-6<br />\n<br />\n新登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=e1e4ed89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n電子表格傳送門-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=98111a14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n實體表格傳送門-&gt; 各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=eefc6d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n或公共屋邨辦事處<br />\n<a href=\"http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F201901%2F29%2FP2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=4baf79f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gia.info.gov.hk/general/201901/29/P2019012900776_303015_1_1548761314431.pdf</a><br />\n或選舉事務處(香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓/九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓)<br />\n<br />\n交表<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=1360e1f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a><br />\n如你持有有效的香港郵政或電子核證服務有限公司的電子核證（個人）證書 &lt;- 呢個基本冇人有，所以唔使試<br />\n<br />\n免費傳真方法 <br />\nHelloFax 免費黑白5張 / FAX.PLUS 免費黑白10張<br />\n<br />\n【教學】選民登記7月2日截止仲未搞？ 教你手機內3分鐘完成手續<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fvotersubmit%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=9eb840d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/06/17/votersubmit/software/android-app/</a>"},{"pid":"93f56457cbf02636692001b0b962f88356d3e0cf","tid":1263983,"uid":251082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15478b468ab35683cf0922fa56c2d3978575ba5e","tid":1263983,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:22:21.000Z","msg":"我想問我搬左屋但未改地址<br />\n我上網上見改地址要係6月前先有今年投票資格<br />\n請問有無其他方法<br />\n<br />\n因為好唔make sence 新登記7月2號前 登記左改地址反而唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548ff8d577ae661fbd4c889265313e8081023f9c","tid":1263983,"uid":251082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15478b468ab35683cf0922fa56c2d3978575ba5e","tid":1263983,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:22:21.000Z","msg":"我想問我搬左屋但未改地址<br />\n我上網上見改地址要係6月前先有今年投票資格<br />\n請問有無其他方法<br />\n<br />\n